<item>
            <title>[LU-7040] Interop 2.7.0&lt;-&gt;master sanity-hsm test_12q: wrong size after overwrite</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7040</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah_lw &amp;lt;wei3.liu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ce341ff0-4584-11e5-9d0e-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/ce341ff0-4584-11e5-9d0e-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_12q failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/mnt/lustre2/d12q.sanity-hsm/f12q.sanity-hsm: wrong size after overwrite: 2097152 != 0
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test log&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Starting copytool agt1 on shadow-25vm10
CMD: shadow-25vm10 mkdir -p /tmp/arc1
CMD: shadow-25vm10 lhsmtool_posix  --daemon --hsm-root /tmp/arc1 --bandwidth 1 /mnt/lustre3 &amp;lt; /dev/null &amp;gt; /logdir/test_logs/2015-08-16/lustre-b2_7-el6_6-x86_64-vs-lustre-master-el7-x86_64--full--2_6_1__3141__-70113007515460-135446/sanity-hsm.test_12q.copytool_log.shadow-25vm10.log 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
 sanity-hsm test_12q: @@@@@@ FAIL: /mnt/lustre2/d12q.sanity-hsm/f12q.sanity-hsm: wrong size after overwrite: 2097152 != 0 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please provide additional information about the failure here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-hsm 12q&lt;/p&gt;</description>
